---
description: Data fetching and mutation rules — useFetch, useMutation, usePaginatedFetch, API proxy.
globs: src/hooks/**,src/features/**,src/app/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Read `.claude/rules/data-fetching.md` for the full data fetching rules.

Key points: `useFetch` for reads, `useMutation` for writes, `usePaginatedFetch` for paginated lists. All requests proxy through `/api/proxy`. API interceptor auto-fires `toastError` on 4xx/5xx — do not double-call.
